comparison added) detects whether the pod template annotation changed.\n4. If the hash hasn't changed (same CA bundle content), `deploymentSpecModified` returns `false` and the update is skipped \u2014 no Patch/Update call is made.\n5. If the CA bundle content changed, the hash differs, `deploymentSpecModified` returns `true`, and the deployment is updated, which triggers a rolling restart because the pod template spec changed.\n\n---\n\n### Commands to build and test\n\n```bash\n# From the repository root:\n\n# 1. Verify it compiles\nmake build\n# or\ngo build ./...\n\n# 2. Run the istiocsr unit tests\ngo test ./pkg/controller/istiocsr/... -v\n\n# 3. Run the full test suite\nmake test\n```", "stop_reason": "end_turn", "session_id": "28bc8e08-8b2b-4a57-baeb-0a1292c0555f", "total_cost_usd": 1.05259675, "usage": {"input_tokens": 6770, "cache_creation_input_tokens": 77351, "cache_read_input_tokens": 742556, "output_tokens": 6561, "server_tool_use": {"web_search_requests": 0, "web_fetch_requests": 0}, "service_tier": "standard", "cache_creation": {"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens": 0, "ephemeral_5m_input_tokens": 77351}, "inference_geo": "", "iterations": [], "speed": "standard"}, "modelUsage": {"claude-opus-4-6": {"inputTokens": 6770, "outputTokens": 6561, "cacheReadInputTokens": 742556, "cacheCreationInputTokens": 77351, "webSearchRequests": 0, "costUSD": 1.05259675, "contextWindow": 200000, "maxOutputTokens": 64000}}, "permission_denials": [], "terminal_reason": "completed", "fast_mode_state": "off", "uuid": "812f7a03-861d-4e76-b9e9-cd23d5c4e1a6", "timestamp": "2026-07-16T14:02:38.365Z"}